runtimeSessions, artifacts. Use imports: integer, sqliteTable, text from drizzle-orm/sqlite-core. Columns must match the plan exactly:\n   - runs: id primary key; runtime/provider/model/adapterType/cwd/task/status/placement/approvalPolicy text not null; timeoutSeconds integer not null; metadataJson text not null; createdAt text not null; startedAt/endedAt nullable text. DB column names use snake_case where in plan: adapter_type, approval_policy, timeout_seconds, metadata_json, created_at, started_at, ended_at.\n   - runEvents: id primary key; type text not null; runId text run_id not null; debateId, participantId, provider, model nullable text; sequence integer not null; payloadJson text payload_json not null; createdAt text created_at not null.\n   - runtimeSessions: id primary key; runId run_id not null; runtime/provider/model/protocol/status text not null; externalSessionKey external_session_key nullable; processId process_id nullable integer; stateJson state_json not null; createdAt created_at not null; updatedAt updated_at nullable.\n   - artifacts: id primary key; runId, debateId, provider, model nullable text; type/path text not null; metadataJson metadata_json text not null; createdAt created_at not null.\n4. Create packages/storage/src/sqlite/database.ts using better-sqlite3 and drizzle-orm/better-sqlite3. Export type SwitchyardSqliteDatabase, interface OpenSqliteStorageResult { sqlite: Database.Database; db: SwitchyardSqliteDatabase }, function openSqliteStorage(path: string). It should open DB, set journal_mode=WAL, run migrate(sqlite), return drizzle(sqlite, { schema }). Migration SQL should create runs, run_events, runtime_sessions, artifacts plus indexes run_events_run_sequence_idx, runtime_sessions_run_id_idx unique, artifacts_run_id_idx.\n5. Create packages/storage/src/index.ts exporting ./sqlite/database.js.\n6. Run `pnpm install` from repo root to update pnpm-lock.yaml. If dependency fetching fails due network/sandbox, rerun with required escalation per environment rules.\n7. Run `pnpm --filter @switchyard/storage typecheck`.\n8. Commit with: git add pnpm-lock.yaml packages/storage && git commit -m \"feat: add local sqlite storage package\"\n\nFinal response format:\nSTATUS: DONE | DONE_WITH_CONCERNS | NEEDS_CONTEXT | BLOCKED\nCHANGED FILES: list paths\nTESTS: commands run and pass/fail\nCOMMIT: commit sha if committed\nNOTES: concise self-review and concerns"}]}}
